title: [CROSS ANGE] - Complete OST (1+2+3) With Extras
description:
First of all, thanks for downloading, this is my first torrent. Hope you like it

Ahem, Ladies and Gentlemen....and my best friend Josh Smith,

Presenting to you,

Cross Ange - Tenshi to Ryuu no Rondo - Complete soundtrack.

This set contains:
1- The first Volume of Cross Ange OST
2- The second volume of Cross Ange OST
3- The third volume of Cross Ange OST
4- Extras

[NOTE]: The Extras were added because the OST 1,2 or 3 Do NOT contain:
1-The Opening Theme 1 "Kaidan no Resistance"
2-The Opening Theme 2 "Sinjitsu no Mokushitoku"
3-The Ending Theme 1 "Rinrei"
4-The Ending Theme 2 "Shuumatsu No Love song"
5-Necessary (Song played in episodes)

So it pretty much concludes that they inserted the episode soundtracks into the packs but sold all the OPs and EDs sperarately. But I looked up for the opening and endings and found the whole volumes. Therefore, with each OP or ED pack, you'll find some extra songs (NOT from Cross Ange).
So you get the WHOLE Cross Ange OST AND extra!
